<div class=3D"col-12 col-md-3">
<div class=3D"post__photo-info">
<div class=3D"post__photo-caption">
<p>SPIN students David Zhu (L to R), Varenya Jain, Will Hunter and Kaiyan W=
ang pose with Olena Kindratenko during the 2nd Annual NCSA Student Research=
 Conference in April, 2024.</p>
</div>
<div class=3D"post__photo-credit">
<p></p>
</div>
